    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "バッチリですよ\nあ……琴乃ちゃんも準備出来たみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All set!\nAh…looks like Kotono-chan’s ready‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.228821206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5306350469
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 12.8000000715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3306347768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3306347768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、よく似合ってるよ……琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it looks good on you…Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6457595348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.1134694099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\n私の衣装も用意してくれていて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Manager-san.\nYou even prepared my costume for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666668653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7059185027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "また五人でやっていくと決めて\nすぐに衣装を注文してくれて、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for ordering the costume\nas soon as we decided we would continue as five again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0913840847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.2697716075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "さすがですわ、{user}さん\n褒めてあげますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Manager-san!\nI'll give you some praise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9666653394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに全員揃うんだ。衣装だって揃えないとな\nすず、今日はセンターをよろしく頼むぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since we were all together. We need matching outfits.\nSuzu‚ I’m counting on you for center today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666653394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.3378440219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ！　五人に戻って新たなスタートを切る\n新生月のテンペストのセンターはこの私！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! The center for the new Moon Tempest‚ making a fresh start\nwith five members‚ is this me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7666653394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "成宮すずこそふさわしいということを\n大観衆に見せつけますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll show the audience that Suzu Narumiya\nis the one who deserves to be here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1666653394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1787740705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、すず。心強いわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ Suzu. I feel reassured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1787740705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.9814724045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "（復活ライブ……不安がないと言ったら嘘になる）\n（けど今は、私が――私達の全力を尽くすだけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The comeback live…It’d be a lie to say I’m not nervous.）\n（But right now‚ I…we…just have to give it our all.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6999986727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4428741532
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.3999986727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ……{user}さん\n行ってきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then…Manager-san‚\nI’m off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3999986727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 83.9164685802
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 83.9164685802
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 84.0915306168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "本日はお越しいただき、本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all so much for coming today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9115393397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 89.8058024801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "五人に戻った私達……新生月のテンペストの\nパフォーマンスを、その目に焼き付けてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please burn the performance of the new Moon Tempest‚\n…back with five members‚ into your eyes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1333264112,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8060.8587903000025,
          "startTime": 97.8666612704
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 99.2989797034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "（……やっぱり、客席がざわめいてる。当然よね）\n（あんなことをした私が、またここに立ってるんだから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…As expected‚ the audience is restless.）\n（After all‚ I’m standing here again after doing such a thing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4666551669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 111.0313380318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、私の――私達のパフォーマンスで）\n（納得してもらうしかない……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ with my…with our performance）\n（…I have no choice but to convince them…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1999885003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 118.2693179525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "聴いて下さい\n――『The One and Only』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please listen.\n――“The One and Only”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2666612704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 123.5116452293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな～、聴いてくれてありがと～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for listening‚ everyone~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3333218336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 132.6333279371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "私達のパフォーマンスは\nどうでし……たか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How was…\n…our performance…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5962937751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 136.8190943318
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 136.8190943318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "（……客席が落ち着かない。それどころかヤジまで）\n（飛んできてる。やっぱり私がちゃんと謝らないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…The audience is uneasy.）\n（…flying towards us. I guess I really need to apologize properly…）",
